[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "さて……事件もようやく一区切りついた。\nいったん状況を整理しておこう",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_01206",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "はい！　まず、ここ連日ベスティラを騒がせていた\n獣人の娘が行方不明になっていた件ですが……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01207",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "これはベスティラ王妃が個人的に\nかわいい獣人の女の子を集めさせていたのが真相でした",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01208",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "綺麗な黒髪の、猫耳の獣人の女の子が特に好きで\nお持ち帰りしたかったと供述しています",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01209",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "綺麗な黒髪で、猫耳……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_01210",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "はぁ、だから謁見した時、耳触らせてとか\n声をかけられたんだね……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_036_01211",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "実行犯の一人である賞金首「ヌルスラの鷹」は\n一度は逃走を図ったもののジョゼによって捕縛",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_01212",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "現在は王宮の牢を一時的に借りて拘束している。\nベスティラ王も厳重に監視すると確約してくれた",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_01213",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "陛下は監察官に協力的なんですか？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_01214",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "はい。一連の事件は何も知らなかった様子で、王妃を\nかわいさのあまり甘やかしすぎたと反省していましたよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01215",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "「俺の代わりに監察本部でこってり絞ってやってくれ。\nどんな結果になろうと俺はあいつを想っている」って",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01216",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "ティム",
		"romanized_name": "Tim",
		"model_path_hash": "9091556145679123684",
		"text": "……いい旦那さんだね。それ聞いたら王妃様も\nなんで裏切っちゃったんだろうって後悔するよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_604_036_01217",
		"still_path_hash": "6387934691877097610",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "まあ、あの豪快な王様は良くも悪くも\n裏表がないっていうか、駆け引きできなそうだしね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_01218",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "攫われてた獣人の女の子たちはどうなるの？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_01219",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "彼女たちは無事で、全員健康だ。\n王妃が手厚くもてなしていたらしい",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_01220",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "基本、被害者家族の元に帰す予定だが\n身寄りのない者や一部の者は帰りたくないと……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_01221",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "酷い扱いは受けてなかったみたいで\nそれは不幸中の幸いですね～",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01222",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "王妃様、愛情だけは本物だったんですね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_01223",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "そうだね、そこは本当に救いだった。\nまぁ誘拐には違いないので、もちろん罪だけども",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01224",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "俺は、誘拐が大嫌いでね。\n王妃は厳しく罰してほしいもんだね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01225",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "……詳しくはこれからブラオールの本部で\n取り調べて判断することになる。それと……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_01226",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "「ヌルスラの鷹」の賞金だ。確認してくれ、ジョゼ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_01227",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "確かに。賞金首捕縛の功績を独り占めして悪いね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01228",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "誰が捕まえたかなどはどうでもいい。\n大切なのは捕まえたという事実だ。協力感謝する",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_01229",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "……ジョゼさん",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_01230",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（さっきのあれって、タイニーさんに言ったら\n　ただじゃおかないって脅迫だよね？　いったい……）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_01231",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "ボスはともかく、私は賞金首を捕まえて一人前に\nなったはずなのに、結局半人前に元通りです……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01232",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "なあに、嬢ちゃんならきっと一人前になれるさ。\nくじけずに頑張るんだよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01233",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "変てこ仮面さんに励まされても嬉しくありません！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01234",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "……あ。\nそういえば、武道会のほうはどうなったんですか？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01235",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 30,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "こっちは大成功でした！　見事勝ち残り、\n賞品として「九偉人図」をもらいましたよ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_01236",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 31,
		"localized_name": "ティム",
		"romanized_name": "Tim",
		"model_path_hash": "9091556145679123684",
		"text": "でも、最後のあの乱入にはびっくりしちゃったなあ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_604_036_01237",
		"still_path_hash": "6387934691877097610",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 32,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "え、乱入？　何があったんですか？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01238",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 33,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "タイニーは残念だったね。あんなすごい戦いを\n仕事で見逃しちゃったんだから",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_036_01239",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 34,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "え、ええ～？　本当に何があったんですか、\n教えてくださいよ～！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01240",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 35,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "まぁまぁ。近いうちに時間を取って、\n武道会のあらましは説明するよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_036_01241",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]